data.description: Great home in The Highlands! 3 bed, 2 full baths, 2 car garage with automatic opener. Large private fenced backyard great for family fun. Vinyl wood plank flooring in living room, ceramic tile in baths and kitchen, with carpet in bedrooms. Corner wood burning fireplace. Property has a security system. New roof was installed in August 2023.
